'''Greenputt''' was a sport played by all kinds of beings in the galaxy. This sport was played on a wide playing field and required each player to hit a tiny ball into a remote hole. The game required a wide range of hitting skills to get the ball in the hole. The major leagues were controlled by the [[Greenputt Governing Council]].<ref name="HNN47">{{HoloNetNewsWeb|47|sports/13314_2.html|Yet Another Greenputt League}}</ref>

The council formed the newest league&mdash;the [[Non-Sentient Professional Greenputt Tour]]&mdash;after discovering three [[Ambria/Legends|Ambrian]] [[Neek (creature)|neek]]s and a [[Taurill/Legends|Taurill]] named [[Bortis]] as capable players.<ref name="HNN47" />

==Major leagues==
*[[Professional Greenputt Tour]] (PGT)<ref name="HNN47" />
*[[Female Professional Greenputt Tour]] (FPGT)<ref name="HNN47" />
*[[Asexual Professional Greenputt Tour]] (APGT)<ref name="HNN47" />
*[[Not-Dead-Yet Professional Greenputt Tour]] (NDYPGT)<ref name="HNN47" />
